# This git repo is rooted at ~/.config, which holds lots of unrelated (and
# sometimes sensitive) app data. Ignore everything by default and only track
# the NixOS configuration, so nothing private is ever accidentally published.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/nixos.png
!/nixos/

# Within the nixos/ tree, keep editor/build cruft out.
nixos/home.nix.save
nixos/result
nixos/result-*

# Video wallpapers are too large for GitHub (the .mp4 files exceed the 100MB
# per-file limit). Track image wallpapers only.
nixos/wallpapers/*.mp4
